<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Low Stock Alert</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333; line-height: 1.6; padding: 20px; background-color: #f9fafb;">

<div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; border-top: 5px solid #ef4444; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">

    <h2 style="color: #ef4444; margin-top: 0;">Low Stock Alert</h2>

    <p>Hello Manager,</p>
    <p>An order was just approved that caused the following items to drop below their required minimum stock thresholds. Please review the inventory and restock as soon as possible.</p>

    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 12px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb; font-size: 14px;">Product Name</th>
            <th style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 12px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb; font-size: 14px;">Location</th>
            <th style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 12px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb; font-size: 14px;">Current Stock</th>
            <th style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 12px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb; font-size: 14px;">Threshold Limit</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        {% for product in products %}
            <tr>
                <td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold;">{{ product.name }}</td>
                <td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: center;">{{ product.location ? product.location.value : 'N/A' }}</td>
                <td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: center; color: #ef4444; font-weight: bold;">{{ product.currentStock }}</td>
                <td style="padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: center; color: #6b7280;">{{ product.lowStockThreshold }}</td>
            </tr>
        {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
        <a href="{{ absolute_url(path('app_stock_index')) }}" style="background-color: #3b82f6; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">
            Go to Stocks Dashboard
        </a>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
